query:
DELETE
            FROM domains
            WHERE domains.id = (SELECT d.id
                                FROM domains d
                                         LEFT JOIN projects p on p.id = d.project_id
                                WHERE (d.project_id IS NULL OR
                                       (
                                           d.project_id = p.id
                                               AND d.project_id = $2
                                               AND p.organization_id = $1
                                           )
                                    )
                                  AND (d.organization_id IS NULL OR
                                       (d.organization_id = $1
                                           AND $2::uuid IS NULL)
                                    )
                                  AND (d.id = $3))
            RETURNING domains.id
